港式茶餐廳， 有茶餐又點心。 中上。
Nice Siu Mei (Chinese BBQ Food) and reasonably priced course meal for 6.
佐敦好少有燒味飯食，咁岩行過見到就入去食下，價錢不算便宜，味道都算ok，不過叉燒有點咸，如果唔係會幾好。個例湯亦都 ok..
好吃！但鵝肉太肥！不敢吃太肥鵝肉，美中不足，从这么老远来到香港就是要享受香港出名美食！说真的香港的美食讓我不能抗拒!尤其是烧類太爱了。

result.adr_address: 22-24 Parkes St, Jordan, Hong Kong
result.name: Ming's Kitchen hk

reviews.text: Roasted pork was too salty and not really tender. Crispy pork also not that crispy
A plate full of bones, everyone gets a soup spoon and chopsticks but us. Nuff said.
Just became one of my favorite places in HK. Food was good (roast duck was so juicy!) and quick. Staffs were very polite. The place was clean, and opened long hours.
Excellent classic HK breakfast: noodles with beef, egg, toast, and meat for HK$30. Staff was polite and spoke English. I would definitely return!

Coming into this diner, it looked clean and food looked tasty. The issue with this restaurant was the service provided from the waitresses. My mom ordered some dim sum. Note: we never order shrimp dumpling ever in dimsum restaurants. And I was there witnessing her order her food. She ordered the shrimp in rice noodle roll. So when her order came, they gave her ha gow, which was the shrimp dumpling. My mom told the waitress that this is not what she ordered. And instead of taking the dish back like a normal waitress, she said "No, I heard you say ha gow two times. You didn't order ha cheong... Eat it instead of wasting it." They neither took the wrong order back nor did they offer to when we were persistent about it. This service is the utmost unprofessional and disrespectful. This is a common theme amongst Hong Kong diners. Unprofessional and disrespectful. We provide the money while they provide the service. At least do things right since we are paying for it. It seems like those who are not Chinese had a decent experience with the staff because my family is and we had such an unprofessional encounter.

result.adr_address: 香港佐敦白加士街22-24號
result.name: Ming's Kitchen hk

reviews.text: La cantine durant notre séjour à Hong Kong. Nous avons vraiment apprécié la carte, les bouchées vapeurs sont au top et pas cher. Le porc laqué est très très bon. La salle est souvent pleine le soir mais le service est vraiment rapide... bravo une très bonne adresse.

早朝便で到着後、朝食を食べに行きました。
本当は近くにある有名店に行くつもりだったのですが、あいにくお休みの為、近くにあったこちらへ突入。予備知識なしで入ってみました。

店内はコンパクトで、いかにも地元という方が大勢おられました。
折角だから香港式の朝食をと思い、サンドイッチと卵焼き？のセットを注文。

濃い塩味になれた日本の田舎者には少々塩気が足りない感じですが、とても優しい味付けでおいしくいただけました。

勿論日本語は通じません。
全部はありませんが、メニューに写真がありますので、指さし注文でも大丈夫だと思います。

比較的すいている時間だったので連れと二人でテーブルを占拠できましたが、この辺の店は相席が当然なので、混んでいるときは覚悟して入って下さい。ただ、地元の皆さんは相席になれているので大騒ぎなどしなければ全く問題ありません。

折角だからと思い、ドリンクは鴛鴦茶を頼んだのですが、正直に言うと私の好みには合いませんでした。合う人はめっちゃ合うと思いますが。
간단하게 먹기 좋은 조던역쪽 로컬식당
Sehe leckeres Essen, guter Preis und freundliche, schnelle Bedienung. Immer wieder gerne!
Roasted pork was too salty and not really tender. Crispy pork also not that crispy
